title: Summary Catalogue of European Sculpture -Fusco- PDF [Slender]
description:
Publisher: The J. Paul Getty Museum; 1 edition (January 8, 1998)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 0892364882
ISBN-13: 978-0892364886

Designed for scholars and students, this book documents every sculpture in the Museum's collection. Reproductions of each piece are accompanied by text that identifies the sculptor, the medium, the dimensions, and the work's date.
